            <p class="tagline">Building the future of cloud-native infrastructure.</p>
            <div class="meta">
                <span><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> San Francisco, CA</span>
                <span><i class="fas fa-link"></i> https://acme.example.com</span>
